NAME
    Pod::Weaver::Plugin::Perinci - Insert POD from Rinci metadata

VERSION
    version 0.09

SYNOPSIS
    In your "weaver.ini":

     [-Perinci]
     ;exclude_modules = REGEX
     ;exclude_files = REGEX

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin inserts POD documentation (generated by Perinci::To::POD).

TODO
